ActBank Act
SubjectFederal Credit Union Conversion Regulations
PrecisFEDERAL CREDIT UNION CONVERSION REGULATIONS in order to specify the process and disclosure required for a federal credit union to change its legal form from a company owned by members to one owned by shareholders. The proposed Regulations contain a series of requirements that must be followed to ensure a fair demutualization process.
